## 🛠️ Development Workflow

### Local Development
```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run development server
npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build
```

### Deployment Pipeline
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Commit] --> B[GitHub]
    B --> C[CI Checks]
    C --> D[Vercel]
    D --> E[Production]
```

